v0.24.0: stalk -> dart hunting rhythm

- predators now CREEP while lining up (stalkSpeedMult) then explode into a fast committed DART (lungeSpeedMult) once prey is in range
- lunge has a duration + cooldown, so it reads as a real pounce, not a constant sprint
- darting straight in overrides the circling; faster movement costs more energy
- creature gains lungeTimer/lungeCd/justKilled state for the upcoming pounce animation
